01:12:20,080 --> 01:12:22,830
我的状态从来没这么好过！ 我的头脑清晰多了！快来！
Oh, I've never felt better! I've never had a clearer mind! Come, come!

924
01:12:23,330 --> 01:12:24,540
你发烧了吗？
Are you running a fever?

925
01:12:25,330 --> 01:12:27,080
我只是看到你太激动了
I am just very excited to see you.

926
01:12:27,620 --> 01:12:30,000
我太高兴了 简直要飞起来了
I'm exalted. The spirits have lifted me so much.

927
01:12:30,080 --> 01:12:32,250
那东西太神奇了 我就知道能实现
Absolutely marvelous…

928
01:12:32,790 --> 01:12:34,410
维克多
Victor…

929
01:12:36,330 --> 01:12:39,450
维克多 请给我一点时间
Victor. Victor.

930
01:14:53,500 --> 01:14:54,870
是谁伤害了你？
Who hurt you?

931
01:14:55,750 --> 01:14:57,500
威廉 你一定要看看这个
I have to show you this, William.

932
01:14:58,540 --> 01:15:00,040
我先整理一下
Let me organize it for you.

933
01:15:00,120 --> 01:15:02,330
我也有东西要给你看
And I have something to show to you.

934
01:15:04,040 --> 01:15:06,000
我跟英国皇家医学会的人聊过了
I've spoken to the Royal Medical Society.

935
01:15:06,700 --> 01:15:09,160
-他们想见你 -现在还不行
-They're interested in seeing you. -No, no, no, not yet.

936
01:15:09,830 --> 01:15:11,080
我还没准备好
I'm not quite ready yet.

937
01:15:12,330 --> 01:15:14,410
我以为这是你一直以来的梦想
I thought that's what you always wanted.

938
01:15:18,410 --> 01:15:19,540
那个男人
The man.

939
01:15:20,500 --> 01:15:22,200
-楼下的那个男人 -你看到他了？
-The man downstairs. -You saw him?

940
01:15:22,910 --> 01:15:25,160
他是病人吗？是被你打伤的吗？
Is he a patient? A victim?

941
01:15:27,080 --> 01:15:29,200
他身上好多伤口 你竟然下手那么重
His wounds. You wounded him like that.

942
01:15:29,290 --> 01:15:32,000
不 伤害他的是这个世界 伊丽莎白
No, no, no. It was the world that hurt him, Elizabeth.

943
01:15:32,080 --> 01:15:33,790
我给了他生命
I… I gave him life.

944
01:15:35,410 --> 01:15:36,620
我给了他生命
I gave him life.

945
01:15:39,000 --> 01:15:40,040
起来
Up, up, up.

946
01:15:40,870 --> 01:15:41,870
来
Come on.

947
01:15:43,830 --> 01:15:45,250
慢着
There, there, there…

948
01:15:45,330 --> 01:15:47,540
他还在适应周围的环境
He's still getting used to his surroundings.

949
01:15:51,120 --> 01:15:53,160
它很强壮 威廉
It is strong, William.

950
01:15:53,250 --> 01:15:55,120
-你成功了 -非常强壮
-You did it. -It's so strong.

951
01:15:55,790 --> 01:15:56,750
你成功了
You did it.

952
01:15:57,330 --> 01:15:59,290
体内所有系统都正常运作
All its systems are functional.

953
01:15:59,370 --> 01:16:00,330
伤口都在愈合
All healing.

954
01:16:01,790 --> 01:16:04,580
愈合的状态不稳定
And the healing is erratic, yes.

955
01:16:05,080 --> 01:16:06,500
但是非同寻常
But exceptional.

956
01:16:14,410 --> 01:16:16,120
他为什么被拴在这里？
Why is he chained here?

957
01:16:16,200 --> 01:16:17,870
为了保护他自己 还有我
For his own safety and for mine,

958
01:16:17,950 --> 01:16:21,620
也更方便给它清洁维护
and it's easy to clean and, uh, maintain it.

959
01:16:21,700 --> 01:16:23,120
很多事它还不懂
And it doesn't know any better.

960
01:16:24,500 --> 01:16:25,500
但你懂
But you do.

961
01:16:28,700 --> 01:16:29,910
哈兰德知道了吗？
Does Harlander know?

962
01:16:32,370 --> 01:16:35,000
我们要在他回来之前把一切准备好…
We have to prepare everything for the moment he returns.

963
01:16:35,080 --> 01:16:37,250
-当然 -…让一切都有模有样
-Of course. -And have everything presentable.

964
01:16:40,750 --> 01:16:42,500
它有智慧吗？
Is it intelligent?

965
01:16:46,370 --> 01:16:48,330
维克多 它有智慧吗？
Victor, is it intelligent?

966
01:17:02,620 --> 01:17:05,250
我无法理解你是怎么做到的
I can't fathom how exactly you did what you did,

967
01:17:05,830 --> 01:17:07,750
但这无疑是一项壮举
but its dimension does not escape me.

968
01:17:10,290 --> 01:17:14,000
维克多 你有没有问过自己
Victor, did you ever ask yourself,

969
01:17:15,040 --> 01:17:16,910
这个人的所有组成部分中
of all the parts that make that man,

970
01:17:17,830 --> 01:17:19,830
哪块是灵魂藏身的地方？
which one holds the soul?

971
01:17:26,450 --> 01:17:27,950
我没问过
No, I didn't.

972
01:17:28,580 --> 01:17:32,040
楼下那头怪物总让人感到不安
There's something so disquieting about that creature down there.

973
01:17:33,200 --> 01:17:36,500
扭曲诡异 像个在哈哈镜里探头探脑的身影
Askew, like a figure peeking around a funhouse mirror.

974
01:17:37,200 --> 01:17:38,450
但很有活力
But animated.

975
01:17:39,290 --> 01:17:40,450
是哪里来的活力？
Animated by what?

976
01:18:45,330 --> 01:18:46,370
痛吗？
Does it hurt?

977
01:18:54,500 --> 01:18:55,450
叶子？
A leaf?

978
01:18:55,950 --> 01:18:56,950
给我的吗？
For me?

979
01:18:57,830 --> 01:18:58,950
谢谢
Thank you.

980
01:19:03,040 --> 01:19:04,370
是不是很美？
Isn't it beautiful?

981
01:19:05,870 --> 01:19:06,830
给我的吗？
This is for me?

982
01:19:08,580 --> 01:19:09,620
我是伊丽莎白
I'm Elizabeth.

983
01:19:11,620 --> 01:19:13,120
会说吗？伊丽莎白
Can you say "Elizabeth"?

984
01:19:14,290 --> 01:19:15,330
伊丽莎白
Elizabeth.

985
01:19:16,620 --> 01:19:19,160
从喉咙里发出声音
My throat makes sounds.

986
01:19:19,750 --> 01:19:20,830
伊丽莎白
Elizabeth.

987
01:19:37,750 --> 01:19:38,910
我要走了
I'm going to go now.

988
01:19:53,750 --> 01:19:56,950
伊丽莎…白
Eliza… beth.

989
01:19:58,830 --> 01:20:00,580
你不该靠近那东西的
You should not go near it.

990
01:20:02,660 --> 01:20:03,540
那东西？
"It"?

991
01:20:05,660 --> 01:20:07,660
没错 那东西
It. Yes.

992
01:20:08,250 --> 01:20:12,370
那东西是活的 但没有智慧的火花
I believe there is life in it, but not the spark of intelligence

993
01:20:12,450 --> 01:20:13,450
我故意这么设计的
that I had intended.

994
01:20:13,540 --> 01:20:15,160
可能不是你想象的那样
Perhaps not as you understand it.

995
01:20:15,250 --> 01:20:16,870
什么地方出了差错
Something went wrong.

996
01:20:16,950 --> 01:20:19,370
阻塞了 缝合了 连通了
A blockage, a suture, a connection.

997
01:20:19,450 --> 01:20:21,950
伟大的维克多·弗兰肯斯坦 还会犯错？
You, the great Victor Frankenstein, you made a mistake?

998
01:20:22,040 --> 01:20:24,250
那头怪物只会一个词 仅有的一个
The Creature knows but one word, and one word alone.

999
01:20:24,330 --> 01:20:26,290
维克多
"Victor, Victor, Victor, Victor."

1000
01:20:26,370 --> 01:20:28,870
只是莫名其妙地机械重复
It just parrots it without rhyme or reason.

1001
01:20:28,950 --> 01:20:31,950
也许在当下 那个词就是他的一切
Perhaps for the time being that word means everything to him.

1002
01:20:32,040 --> 01:20:35,370
要是重生后的他 获得活力的源泉其实更简单
What if in being anew, the spirit that animates him is simpler,

1003
01:20:35,450 --> 01:20:36,580
-更纯粹… -纯粹？
-purer-- -Purer?

1004
01:20:36,660 --> 01:20:38,540
比普通人的更纯粹呢？
Purer than that of the common man?

1005
01:20:43,290 --> 01:20:44,950
要是他不受制于原罪
What if, unrestrained by sin,

1006
01:20:45,040 --> 01:20:47,870
而造物主为这具伤痕累累的血肉之躯 直接注入了生气呢？
our creator's breath came into its wounded flesh directly?

1007
01:20:47,950 --> 01:20:50,080
天啊 伊丽莎白
Good God, Elizabeth.

1008
01:20:51,910 --> 01:20:54,040
要是我强迫自己信了你这话
If I could force myself to believe it,

1009
01:20:54,120 --> 01:20:58,160
我会觉得你是不是被这东西吸引了
it would be my inclination to see attraction in you for that thing.

1010
01:20:58,250 --> 01:20:59,620
好好理解一下
Understanding.

1011
01:21:00,620 --> 01:21:01,910
他的眼中有痛苦的情绪
In those eyes I saw pain,

1012
01:21:02,000 --> 01:21:04,040
没有智慧 何来痛苦？
and what is pain if not evidence of intelligence?

1013
01:21:04,120 --> 01:21:05,250
那我的痛苦算什么？
What about my pain?

1014
01:21:05,910 --> 01:21:07,450
被你拒绝算什么？
What about what you have denied me?

1015
01:21:08,910 --> 01:21:10,500
我的心想要什么？
What my heart wants…

1016
01:21:11,870 --> 01:21:12,910
你的心？
Your heart?

1017
01:21:16,330 --> 01:21:17,660
所有人体结构中
Of all the human anatomy,

1018
01:21:17,750 --> 01:21:20,330
只有心最难捉摸
that is the organ furthest from your understanding.

1019
01:21:21,330 --> 01:21:23,290
男爵 只有怪物会扮演上帝
Only monsters play God, Baron.

1020
01:21:29,250 --> 01:21:31,250
比普通人更纯粹
Purer than the common man, hmm?

1021
01:21:36,540 --> 01:21:38,700
不知怎的 我成了坏人
And I, somehow, the villain. Mm-hmm.

1022
01:21:40,870 --> 01:21:42,620
你的心很纯粹？
Your heart is pure?

1023
01:21:43,370 --> 01:21:44,910
我向你保证 并非如此
I assure you it isn't.

1024
01:21:45,410 --> 01:21:47,120
我知道 因为是我亲手放进去的
I should know. I put it there.

1025
01:21:47,620 --> 01:21:48,450
上去
Up.

1026
01:21:59,790 --> 01:22:00,950
再试一下
Let us try again.

1027
01:22:04,200 --> 01:22:05,290
腿伸出来
Now give me your leg.

1028
01:22:06,160 --> 01:22:07,000
腿！
Leg!

1029
01:22:08,500 --> 01:22:09,500
腿伸出来！
Give me your leg!

1030
01:22:10,370 --> 01:22:12,750
没有智慧 何来痛苦？
Pain is evidence of intelligence, is it not?

1031
01:22:13,330 --> 01:22:14,790
行 测试一下这个说法吧
Well, let's test the theory.

1032
01:22:15,620 --> 01:22:17,450
腿伸出来！
Give me your leg!

1033
01:22:18,200 --> 01:22:19,120
腿！
Leg!

1034
01:22:20,080 --> 01:22:21,000
腿！
Leg!

1035
01:22:21,080 --> 01:22:22,290
快点！
Come on!

1036
01:22:22,950 --> 01:22:24,160
伸出来 你个野兽！
Give it to me, you beast!

1037
01:22:25,830 --> 01:22:28,330
腿伸出来！
Give me your leg!

1038
01:22:30,040 --> 01:22:31,040
腿！
Leg!

1039
01:22:34,620 --> 01:22:35,700
维克多！
Victor!

1040
01:22:37,250 --> 01:22:38,910
维克多！
Victor!

1041
01:22:41,370 --> 01:22:43,200
维克多！
Victor!

1042
01:22:43,290 --> 01:22:46,290
维克多！
Victor! Victor!

1043
01:22:46,910 --> 01:22:47,950
维克多 怎么了？
What is it, Victor?

1044
01:22:49,290 --> 01:22:50,250
来
Come. Come.

1045
01:22:51,540 --> 01:22:53,910
我失败了 我犯了大错
I failed. I made a mistake.

1046
01:22:54,660 --> 01:22:56,660
-你没有失败 我看过你的图纸了 -失败了
-No, you didn't fail. I saw your papers. -I did.

1047
01:22:56,750 --> 01:22:58,790
-非常完美 -那头怪物极其危险
-It's perfect. -The Creature is extremely dangerous.

1048
01:22:58,870 --> 01:23:00,620
没有…维克多
There's not… Victor.

1049
01:23:01,120 --> 01:23:03,120
我们等哈兰德回来 再一起讨论吧
Let's wait for Harlander and discuss together.

1050
01:23:03,200 --> 01:23:05,540
威廉 有件事我得告诉你
William, there is something you should know.

1051
01:23:06,330 --> 01:23:07,620
我得给你看一下
Something I have to show you.

1052
01:23:13,540 --> 01:23:16,370
-哈兰德… -那头怪物突然暴怒 把他杀了
-Ha-- Harlander… -In a fit of rage, he killed him.

1053
01:23:22,700 --> 01:23:25,870
这下你知道 我为什么没有及时告诉你了吧？
Do you understand now why I was hesitant to share this with you?

1054
01:23:26,500 --> 01:23:28,200
当然也不敢让伊丽莎白知道
And certainly not with Elizabeth.

1055
01:23:31,830 --> 01:23:33,500
那现在怎么办？
S… So what's to be done now?

1056
01:23:34,120 --> 01:23:34,950
什么？
What?

1057
01:23:35,040 --> 01:23:36,660
-现在怎么办？ -你说怎么办？
-What's to be done? -"What's to be done"?

1058
01:23:36,750 --> 01:23:38,450
你得带伊丽莎白回维也纳
You must take Elizabeth back to Vienna.

1059
01:23:38,540 --> 01:23:41,790
就说出了急事 必须马上走
Tell her something urgent came up and you have to leave immediately.

1060
01:23:41,870 --> 01:23:43,250
千万别让她知道
Keep her in the dark.

1061
01:23:44,540 --> 01:23:45,540
这是为了保护她
For her own safety.

1062
01:23:46,160 --> 01:23:47,580
必须照我说的办
You have to do as I say.

1063
01:23:47,660 --> 01:23:50,450
我们很快就回来 但现在只能先走
We'll be back in no time. But for now, this is for the best.

1064
01:23:51,700 --> 01:23:53,750
请上马车吧
Now get in the carriage, please.

1065
01:24:06,790 --> 01:24:08,910
你觉得那头怪物能活多久？
The Creature, what's its lifespan, you think?

1066
01:24:09,910 --> 01:24:12,660
必然没多久
Brief. Very brief, I'm sure.

1067
01:24:59,370 --> 01:25:01,120
我有种很坏的预感
I have the most terrible feeling.

1068
01:25:05,160 --> 01:25:06,040
怎么了？
What is it?

1069
01:25:07,660 --> 01:25:08,950
让马车回头
Turn the carriage around.

1070
01:25:10,080 --> 01:25:11,500
你一个人去维也纳吧
You go to Vienna.

1071
01:25:12,830 --> 01:25:15,580
让马车回头 否则我就跳车 他要杀了他
Turn the carriage around or I will jump. He's going to kill him.

1072
01:25:25,500 --> 01:25:26,580
说个词吧
Say one word.

1073
01:25:27,120 --> 01:25:28,580
再说一个 随便什么
One word more. Anything.

1074
01:25:29,580 --> 01:25:30,580
你说了 我就不杀你
Make me save you.

1075
01:25:35,910 --> 01:25:36,950
维克多
-Victor. -Mm-hmm.

1076
01:25:44,870 --> 01:25:46,950
伊丽莎白
Elizabeth.

1077
01:26:27,500 --> 01:26:30,950
维克多！
Victor! Victor!

1078
01:26:36,700 --> 01:26:38,620
维克多！
Victor!

1079
01:26:39,330 --> 01:26:41,620
维克多！
Victor!

1080
01:27:31,450 --> 01:27:33,700
但故事并未结束
But that was not the end of it.

1081
01:27:33,790 --> 01:27:37,080
我试着创造生命 结果造就了死亡
In seeking life, I created death.

1082
01:27:43,330 --> 01:27:45,950
看来又要和他们聊聊了
It would seem I need to address my men again.

1083
01:27:50,290 --> 01:27:51,120
别担心
Don't worry.

1084
01:27:52,000 --> 01:27:52,950
他们会听我的话的
They'll listen to me.

1085
01:27:57,200 --> 01:28:00,450
住手！别伤害他！我在这里
No, no, stop! Do not harm him! I'm here.

1086
01:28:00,950 --> 01:28:01,950
带走我吧
Take me.

1087
01:28:02,870 --> 01:28:04,040
来吧 野兽
Go on, beast.

1088
01:28:04,120 --> 01:28:07,580
把我俩都杀了 证明造你的人说的都是真的
Kill us both. Confirm your maker's tale.

1089
01:28:13,500 --> 01:28:18,040
造我的人 说了他的故事
My maker… told his tale.

1090
01:28:23,870 --> 01:28:26,660
那我也来说说我的
Then I will tell you mine.

1091
01:28:30,160 --> 01:28:33,080
（第二部分 那头怪物的故事）

1092
01:28:42,790 --> 01:28:48,410
维克多！
Victor!

1093
01:28:48,500 --> 01:28:52,830
我反复呼唤你的名字 终于发现这里只有我
I called your name and understood I was alone.

1094
01:32:52,870 --> 01:32:54,200
-那是什么？ -开枪！
-What is that? -Shoot at it!

1095
01:32:54,290 --> 01:32:55,120
开枪！
Shoot it!

1096
01:33:00,950 --> 01:33:02,330
打到了吗？
Did you get it?

1097
01:33:05,620 --> 01:33:06,700
去哪了？
Where is it?

1098
01:33:27,080 --> 01:33:28,910
身上的伤口愈合了
My wounds had healed.

1099
01:33:31,910 --> 01:33:35,700
但我觉得寒冷刺骨
But I felt cold, so cold.

1100
01:35:08,580 --> 01:35:10,540
-能把火生起来吗？ -好
-Can you start the fire? -All right.

1101
01:35:10,620 --> 01:35:12,540
我会尽快把畜栏修好
And I'll repair the corral as soon as I can.

1102
01:35:19,410 --> 01:35:20,950
你没事吧 打到了吗？
You all right, then? Did you get it?

1103
01:35:21,040 --> 01:35:23,370
没有 我们到处看了 就是找不到
Nah, we looked everywhere. Couldn't find that thing.

1104
01:35:23,450 --> 01:35:25,080
虽然我们朝它开了两枪
Though we shot at it two times.

1105
01:35:25,160 --> 01:35:27,330
血迹在离这里一公里多的地方消失了
Blood trail died about a mile from here.

1106
01:35:27,410 --> 01:35:29,250
好 进来吧
All right. Come in. Come in.

1107
01:35:29,830 --> 01:35:34,040
我们跟了它一段时间 接着它就消失了
We followed it for a while and then it disappeared. Gone.

1108
01:35:34,120 --> 01:35:36,120
那是什么东西？熊吗？
What was it? Was it a bear?

1109
01:35:36,200 --> 01:35:39,500
不是熊 也不是人类 我从没见过那样的东西
That was no bear or human. I've never seen anything like it.

1110
01:35:39,580 --> 01:35:40,950
那么是幽灵吗？
Was it a ghost, then?

1111
01:35:41,040 --> 01:35:44,290
不是 它流血了 说明它有血肉 有骨头
It was no ghost. We drew blood. It was flesh and bone.

1112
01:35:44,370 --> 01:35:45,620
来这边
Come, come. Over here.

1113
01:35:45,700 --> 01:35:47,120
你还看到了什么
Tell me more about what you saw.

1114
01:35:47,200 --> 01:35:50,120
安娜玛丽亚 带祖父去壁炉边
Anna-Maria, take your grandfather over by the fireplace.

1115
01:35:50,200 --> 01:35:51,700
让他暖一暖
Make sure he's comfortable.

1116
01:35:52,790 --> 01:35:54,120
到这边来 祖父
Over here, Grandfather.

1117
01:35:56,370 --> 01:35:58,410
我们钻到了森林深处 还是没找到它
We went deep into the forest. Couldn't find it.

1118
01:36:04,620 --> 01:36:06,000
会抓到它的
We will get it.

1119
01:36:06,080 --> 01:36:07,660
-就是要花些时间 -好
-It'll take time. -Yeah.

1120
01:36:08,620 --> 01:36:10,410
安娜玛丽亚 过来
Anna-Maria, come.

1121
01:36:10,910 --> 01:36:12,750
宝贝 来带我出去
Come, love. Help me outside.

1122
01:36:23,370 --> 01:36:25,370
那位老人触动了我
The old man moved me.

1123
01:36:29,750 --> 01:36:32,700
他失明的双目充满智慧
And his unseeing eyes were full of wisdom.

1124
01:36:45,540 --> 01:36:47,620
这些人会发出一种声音
These people possessed a sound.

1125
01:36:49,080 --> 01:36:50,910
用来和彼此
Used it to tell each other

1126
01:36:51,000 --> 01:36:54,500
交流感受和想法
about feelings and ideas.

1127
01:36:56,160 --> 01:36:58,370
他们把这种声音叫言语
They called them words.

1128
01:37:01,700 --> 01:37:02,790
注意看
Pay attention.

1129
01:37:03,660 --> 01:37:04,580
这是什么？
What is this?

1130
01:37:05,160 --> 01:37:06,160
一个男孩
A boy.

1131
01:37:07,410 --> 01:37:09,200
-再说一遍 -一个男孩
-And again. -A boy.

1132
01:37:10,200 --> 01:37:11,410
很好 孩子
Very good, my child.

1133
01:37:12,910 --> 01:37:13,870
这个呢？
And this?

1134
01:37:13,950 --> 01:37:16,000
一只…一只眼睛
An… An eye.

1135
01:37:16,790 --> 01:37:18,620
-再说一遍 -一只眼睛
-And again. -An eye.

1136
01:37:18,700 --> 01:37:21,700
很好 乖孩子
Yeah. Well done. Well done, my girl.

1137
01:37:21,790 --> 01:37:23,790
-眼睛 -这个呢？
-Eye. -And this one?

1138
01:37:23,870 --> 01:37:24,830
手
The hand.

1139
01:37:24,910 --> 01:37:26,870
-很好 -手
-Very good. -Hand.

1140
01:37:27,790 --> 01:37:28,700
来搭把手
Give us a hand.

1141
01:37:28,790 --> 01:37:31,160
用绳子把最大的捆住带回去
Tie a rope around the biggest one back there.

1142
01:37:31,250 --> 01:37:33,660
我渴望加入这个家庭
I longed to be part of this family.

1143
01:37:34,330 --> 01:37:36,370
冬天之前要再多储备一些柴火
We'll need more kindling before the winter.

1144
01:37:36,450 --> 01:37:38,000
我们得跑几趟
We'll take a few trips.

1145
01:37:38,620 --> 01:37:40,540
渴望帮他们的忙
To be their benefactor.

1146
01:37:41,120 --> 01:37:42,830
需要大一点的树干来搭这个
We'll need larger trunks for the structure.

1147
01:37:42,910 --> 01:37:43,750
好
All right.

1148
01:37:43,830 --> 01:37:46,750
我能为他们做点什么呢？
What could I possibly do for them?

1149
01:37:52,290 --> 01:37:55,250
安娜玛丽亚！父亲！
Anna-Maria! Father!

1150
01:37:55,330 --> 01:37:57,450
快来看啊！
Come! Come and see!

1151
01:37:59,500 --> 01:38:01,080
看啊 安娜玛丽亚！
Look, Anna-Maria!

1152
01:38:01,160 --> 01:38:02,870
看 还有呢！快看！
Look, there's more! Look!

1153
01:38:05,080 --> 01:38:06,620
这会是谁送来的？
Who could have done this?

1154
01:38:09,870 --> 01:38:11,660
是森林精灵
The Spirit of the Forest.

1155
01:38:13,290 --> 01:38:14,540
我们得谢谢他
We should thank him.

1156
01:38:16,290 --> 01:38:17,330
谢谢你
Thank you.

1157
01:38:17,410 --> 01:38:20,120
说“谢谢你 森林精灵”
Say, "Thank you, Spirit of the Forest."

1158
01:38:20,200 --> 01:38:23,250
谢谢你 森林精灵
Thank you. Thank you, Spirit of the Forest.

1159
01:38:23,330 --> 01:38:24,330
谢谢
Thank you.

1160
01:38:25,370 --> 01:38:26,870
来吧 看这里
Come. Look over here.

1161
01:38:33,500 --> 01:38:34,540
谢谢你
Thank you.

1162
01:38:36,620 --> 01:38:40,250
从此以后 我就成了 他们看不见的守护者
From then on, I became their invisible guardian.

1163
01:38:41,160 --> 01:38:43,250
森林精灵
The Spirit of the Forest.

1164
01:38:44,040 --> 01:38:49,160
他们也不时对我释放小小的善意
And on occasion, they too extended a small kindness towards me.

1165
01:38:50,330 --> 01:38:52,540
送上衣服、面包
Clothes, bread.

1166
01:38:54,750 --> 01:38:56,790
在那段时光
And for a moment,

1167
01:38:57,370 --> 01:39:00,410
极为短暂的时光
a brief, brief moment,

1168
01:39:01,200 --> 01:39:03,540
我和这个世界相安无事
the world and I were at peace.

1169
01:39:11,700 --> 01:39:13,290
跟上
Come along. Come along.

1170
01:39:13,370 --> 01:39:14,250
进去吧 对
In you go. Yeah.

1171
01:39:14,330 --> 01:39:15,700
记得关门
Make sure you close that gate.

1172
01:39:15,790 --> 01:39:17,580
是谁做的呢？
Who could have done this?

1173
01:39:17,660 --> 01:39:19,790
森林精灵吧
The Spirit of the Forest, eh?

1174
01:39:20,910 --> 01:39:21,910
我知道了
I got it.

1175
01:39:24,080 --> 01:39:28,790
“最终 这个骄傲的年轻男子
"And in the end, the proud young man

1176
01:39:28,870 --> 01:39:32,080
再也找不到他丢失的那只手了
could never find his missing hand."

1177
01:39:32,160 --> 01:39:36,330
它变成了石头 他的财富消失了
"It turned to stone, his fortune gone,

1178
01:39:36,410 --> 01:39:40,000
他的骄傲 他的土地 都失去了”
and he lost his pride and lost his land."

1179
01:39:46,080 --> 01:39:48,200
非常好 宝贝
Very good, my dear.

1180
01:39:48,290 --> 01:39:51,200
读得真棒 再读下这个吧
Beautifully read. Now try this one.

1181
01:40:01,250 --> 01:40:02,250
狼来了
Wolves.

1182
01:40:47,700 --> 01:40:48,700
某个想法
An idea,

1183
01:40:49,830 --> 01:40:52,120
某种感觉 在我心中愈发清晰
a feeling became clear to me.

1184
01:40:54,910 --> 01:40:57,450
猎人并不憎恨狼
The hunter did not hate the wolf.

1185
01:40:58,330 --> 01:41:00,700
狼并不憎恨羊
The wolf did not hate the sheep.

1186
01:41:06,410 --> 01:41:09,330
但相互之间的暴力冲突无可避免
But violence felt inevitable between them.

1187
01:41:10,330 --> 01:41:15,540
我想 也许这正是世界的法则
Perhaps, I thought, this was the way of the world.

1188
01:41:16,660 --> 01:41:19,790
你成为猎物 被杀
It would hunt you and kill you

1189
01:41:21,120 --> 01:41:23,370
只是因为你的身份
just for being who you are.

1190
01:41:26,080 --> 01:41:28,410
父亲 我月末就会把羊卖掉
The sheep will be sold by the end of the month, Father.

1191
01:41:29,250 --> 01:41:31,910
然后带着你 阿尔玛和安娜玛丽亚去镇上住
Then I'll take you, Alma and Anna-Maria into town.

1192
01:41:32,700 --> 01:41:33,870
我们要上山
We'll go into the mountains,

1193
01:41:33,950 --> 01:41:36,000
去猎几头狼 冬末回来
hunt the wolves and be back at the end of winter.

1194
01:41:36,080 --> 01:41:41,040
我每年冬天都在这里祈祷 今年也一样
I pray here alone every winter and this year will be no different.

1195
01:41:41,120 --> 01:41:43,750
父亲 求你了 听劝吧
Please, Father, listen to reason.

1196
01:41:43,830 --> 01:41:47,330
你们该怎么做就怎么做 我也一样
You do what you must and so will I.

1197
01:41:51,160 --> 01:41:52,620
老顽固
You stubborn old goat.

1198
01:41:55,250 --> 01:41:57,620
现在只有你和我了 森林精灵
It's just you and I now, Spirit.

1199
01:41:58,500 --> 01:42:00,000
就你和我了
Just you and I.

1200
01:42:00,580 --> 01:42:05,200
我已经构想了无数种方式
And I had formed in my imagination many ways

1201
01:42:05,290 --> 01:42:07,950
我要在这个老头面前现身
I would present myself to the old man.

1202
01:42:09,620 --> 01:42:11,000
他会怕我？
Would he fear me?

1203
01:42:12,410 --> 01:42:13,580
欢迎我？
Welcome me?

1204
01:42:15,040 --> 01:42:16,250
还是会赶我走呢？
Turn me away?

1205
01:42:23,750 --> 01:42:24,580
谁在那里？
Who goes there?

1206
01:42:30,910 --> 01:42:35,160
上前一步 我进入了完全不同的世界
With a single step, I entered a different world.

1207
01:42:36,370 --> 01:42:38,910
曾经我只能远远观望的世界
One I had only seen from afar.

1208
01:42:41,200 --> 01:42:42,910
到底是谁？
Please, who is it?

1209
01:42:43,540 --> 01:42:44,540
出个声吧
Answer me.

1210
01:42:45,910 --> 01:42:46,790
告诉我
Tell me.

1211
01:42:47,410 --> 01:42:48,910
你来干什么的？
Why are you here?

1212
01:42:51,330 --> 01:42:52,200
路过
Travel.

1213
01:42:52,790 --> 01:42:54,580
亲爱的过客 欢迎你
Welcome, dear traveler.

1214
01:42:55,620 --> 01:43:01,410
请你自己找把椅子 不要觉得我怠慢了你
Do not think me ungrateful for the company if I ask you to procure a chair.

1215
01:43:01,500 --> 01:43:06,250
我没法周到待客
I… I find it difficult being a good host.

1216
01:43:06,330 --> 01:43:07,160
没错
Yes.

1217
01:43:07,250 --> 01:43:10,830
我的眼睛看不见
My… My sight has failed me.

1218
01:43:12,660 --> 01:43:16,660
桌上有面包和白兰地
But there is bread and brandy on the table.

1219
01:43:16,750 --> 01:43:17,870
请自行享用
Pray help yourself.

1220
01:43:20,080 --> 01:43:21,540
白兰地？
Bran… dy?

1221
01:43:22,870 --> 01:43:24,330
听你说话
Your language.

1222
01:43:25,000 --> 01:43:28,330
好像不大流利
You have a hard time speaking it.

1223
01:43:28,910 --> 01:43:31,000
你是不是从别的地方来的？
Are you not from these parts?

1224
01:43:36,790 --> 01:43:37,660
你害怕吗？
Are you afraid?

1225
01:43:39,620 --> 01:43:40,870
不用怕
No need to be.

1226
01:43:45,870 --> 01:43:47,500
你在怕什么？
What are you afraid of?

1227
01:43:48,250 --> 01:43:49,290
什么都怕
-Everything.

1228
01:43:49,370 --> 01:43:50,200
你的…
-Your…

1229
01:43:50,790 --> 01:43:53,250
你的手好冷
Your hands are frozen

1230
01:43:53,790 --> 01:43:57,450
你还受伤了
and you've been hurt, have you not?

1231
01:43:57,540 --> 01:43:58,410
受伤？
Hurt?

1232
01:43:58,500 --> 01:44:05,250
没错 你的手上和脸上都有伤疤
Yes. Your hands and face have scars

1233
01:44:05,330 --> 01:44:06,950
你还穿着制服
and you are wearing uniform.

1234
01:44:07,040 --> 01:44:08,870
是在战斗中受的伤吗？
Were you injured in battle?

1235
01:44:12,120 --> 01:44:12,950
你一直
You were hiding

1236
01:44:14,080 --> 01:44:16,500
躲在磨坊齿轮里面 对吧？
in the mill gears, were you not?

1237
01:44:21,080 --> 01:44:24,250
对 你就是森林精灵
Yeah. Yeah. The Spirit of the Forest.

1238
01:44:24,330 --> 01:44:25,160
没错
Yes.

1239
01:44:26,040 --> 01:44:28,500
我看不到你的面容
I cannot judge of your countenance,

1240
01:44:29,330 --> 01:44:31,660
但听你的嗓音
but there is something in your voice

1241
01:44:31,750 --> 01:44:35,620
你肯定很善良
which persuades me of your goodwill and kindness.

1242
01:44:36,120 --> 01:44:37,200
善良？
-Kindness? -Mm.

1243
01:44:39,620 --> 01:44:41,700
留下来吧
Stay with me.

1244
01:44:43,040 --> 01:44:45,620
你可以吃我的东西 烤我的火
Share my food and fire.

1245
01:44:46,120 --> 01:44:50,000
我有的不多 但能跟你分享 我会很高兴的
I would be delighted to share what little I have with you

1246
01:44:50,080 --> 01:44:53,660
有你陪着我 对我也大有好处
and would be greatly helped by your companionship.

1247
01:44:54,330 --> 01:44:57,450
你可以读书给我听
And you… you could read to me.

1248
01:44:57,950 --> 01:44:58,870
读书？
-Read? -Mm.

1249
01:45:00,120 --> 01:45:05,870
把这里当成自己家 把我当成朋友
Make this your home and I your friend.

1250
01:45:07,500 --> 01:45:08,370
朋友
Friend.

1251
01:45:13,750 --> 01:45:14,750
朋友
Friend.

1252
01:45:23,330 --> 01:45:24,160
朋友
Friends.

1253
01:45:25,580 --> 01:45:29,620
就是在那时 我读到了我生命中第一个故事
And it was then that I read my first story,

1254
01:45:30,620 --> 01:45:33,160
也是《圣经》中的第一个故事
and it was the first story.

1255
01:45:34,370 --> 01:45:39,330
故事的主人公是一个名叫亚当的男子 和名叫夏娃的女子
I read about a man named Adam and a woman named Eve,

1256
01:45:40,200 --> 01:45:43,580
他们住在人类的第一个乐园里
about their time in the first garden.

1257
01:45:44,450 --> 01:45:47,660
我读到了两座城市崛起 相互竞争
I read about the rise of rival cities

1258
01:45:48,160 --> 01:45:49,910
一座高塔倒塌
and the collapse of a tower

1259
01:45:50,410 --> 01:45:52,750
上帝震怒毁城
and the wrath of a God.

1260
01:45:53,330 --> 01:45:57,750
我读到人类斗巨龙
And I read about men that fought dragons

1261
01:45:57,830 --> 01:46:00,500
最终失去一切
and men who lost everything.

1262
01:46:01,370 --> 01:46:03,040
时光流逝
And time passed

1263
01:46:03,620 --> 01:46:06,870
如秋叶飘落
and fell away with the leaves of autumn.

1264
01:46:18,540 --> 01:46:21,660
亲爱的朋友 你见过下雪吗？
Have you never seen the snow, my dear friend?

1265
01:46:23,330 --> 01:46:27,080
大雪荡涤一切 让世界焕然一新
It makes the world clean… and new.

1266
01:46:33,000 --> 01:46:37,830
“吾乃奥兹曼迪亚斯 万王之王
"My name is Ozymandias, King of Kings."

1267
01:46:38,330 --> 01:46:41,660
盖世功业 敢叫天公折服
"Look on my works, ye Mighty, and despair."

1268
01:46:42,950 --> 01:46:45,200
此外无一物
"No thing beside remains."

1269
01:46:45,750 --> 01:46:50,080
但见废墟周围 寂寞平沙空莽莽
"Round the decay of that colossal wreck, boundless and bare."

1270
01:46:50,160 --> 01:46:53,870
伸向荒凉的四方
"The lone and level sands stretch far away."

1271
01:46:55,500 --> 01:46:58,450
吾乃奥兹曼迪亚斯”
"My name is Ozymandias…"

1272
01:47:05,200 --> 01:47:07,700
世上哪里的书比这里还多？
Are there more books than this in the world?

1273
01:47:09,750 --> 01:47:11,620
肯定还有一些地方
A few more, I'm sure.

1274
01:47:12,370 --> 01:47:13,790
不是这里
Not here.

1275
01:47:15,830 --> 01:47:19,250
左边最后 就拿那本
Last book on the left. Take it.

1276
01:47:19,330 --> 01:47:21,370
那本还没读过
We haven't got to it.

1277
01:47:21,450 --> 01:47:24,200
弥尔顿的《失乐园》
Paradise Lost, Milton.

1278
01:47:24,290 --> 01:47:27,200
人类对上帝有疑问
Man has questions for God.

1279
01:47:27,950 --> 01:47:30,330
就连上帝自己也有疑问
Even God has questions.

1280
01:47:31,040 --> 01:47:35,750
我觉得上帝也想得到答案 所以才会派来自己的儿子
I think he wanted answers and that is why he sent us his son.

1281
01:47:36,330 --> 01:47:38,790
或许他很想了解死亡
Death probably intrigued him.

1282
01:47:39,410 --> 01:47:40,290
了解受苦受难
Suffering.

1283
01:47:41,450 --> 01:47:44,410
我想知道我是谁
I want to know who I am.

1284
01:47:45,160 --> 01:47:46,910
我从哪里来？
Where do I come from?

1285
01:47:47,450 --> 01:47:52,750
上帝拿走了你的记忆 而我多么希望我的记忆也被带走
God took your memory just as I wish he would take mine away.

1286
01:47:54,200 --> 01:47:57,500
多年前 我拿走了某个人的生命
Many years ago, I took a man's life.

1287
01:47:58,160 --> 01:47:59,080
那是个好人
A good man.

1288
01:47:59,620 --> 01:48:02,040
自那时起 我一直在赎罪
And I have been atoning for it since.

1289
01:48:04,330 --> 01:48:05,200
试着原谅
Forgive.

1290
01:48:06,120 --> 01:48:06,950
试着忘记
Forget.

1291
01:48:07,660 --> 01:48:09,580
智慧真正的试金石
The true measure of wisdom.

1292
01:48:10,790 --> 01:48:12,910
是知道自己受了伤害
To know you have been harmed,

1293
01:48:13,000 --> 01:48:15,160
知道被谁伤害
by whom you have been harmed,

1294
01:48:15,250 --> 01:48:18,120
然后选择让一切烟消云散
and choose to let it all fade.

1295
01:48:19,200 --> 01:48:23,160
但记不起来的东西 要怎么忘记
But I cannot forget what I cannot remember.

1296
01:48:23,250 --> 01:48:24,660
你什么都记不起来吗？
Do you recall nothing?

1297
01:48:30,120 --> 01:48:32,830
在睡梦中
In my dreams…

1298
01:48:35,620 --> 01:48:38,870
我…能窥见记忆
…I… see memories.

1299
01:48:42,200 --> 01:48:43,750
各种各样的人
Different men.

1300
01:48:46,200 --> 01:48:48,790
都是…一些片断
All… pieces.

1301
01:48:56,000 --> 01:48:57,000
我…
I…

1302
01:48:59,330 --> 01:49:03,080
我记得有火 有水
I remember f… fire and water.

1303
01:49:06,250 --> 01:49:08,160
脚下有沙子
And sand under my feet.

1304
01:49:15,330 --> 01:49:16,580
还有一个词
And a word.

1305
01:49:19,250 --> 01:49:20,750
就一个词
A single word.

1306
01:49:23,200 --> 01:49:24,500
什么词？
What is it?

1307
01:49:27,290 --> 01:49:28,290
维克多
Victor.

1308
01:49:29,580 --> 01:49:30,750
去找到它
Go to it.

1309
01:49:31,790 --> 01:49:32,910
维克多
The word.

1310
01:50:09,750 --> 01:50:11,790
然后我终于体会到了
And then I learned it.

1311
01:50:12,700 --> 01:50:14,910
真相的可怖
The horror of the truth.

1312
01:50:20,700 --> 01:50:23,870
我明白了 自己一无是处
I understood that I was nothing.

1313
01:50:25,160 --> 01:50:26,370
是个可怜虫
A wretch.

1314
01:50:27,080 --> 01:50:28,370
是块不起眼的污渍
A blot.

1315
01:50:28,910 --> 01:50:32,040
甚至算不上是人类
Not even of the same nature as man.

1316
01:50:35,250 --> 01:50:37,040
这种痛苦缠绕着我
This hurt clung to my mind.

1317
01:50:39,750 --> 01:50:41,450
永不消散
It never let go.

1318
01:51:24,870 --> 01:51:26,450
然后我看见了
Then I saw it.

1319
01:51:28,080 --> 01:51:29,450
你的名字
Your name.

1320
01:51:30,200 --> 01:51:33,700
“维克多·弗兰肯斯坦”
"Victor Frankenstein."

1321
01:51:33,790 --> 01:51:35,750
知道了到哪里能找到你
And where to find you.

1322
01:51:57,000 --> 01:51:58,250
不！
No!

1323
01:51:59,500 --> 01:52:01,250
不！
No!

1324
01:53:10,290 --> 01:53:11,700
你回来了
You came back.

1325
01:53:11,790 --> 01:53:14,080
我知道我是谁了
I found what I am.

1326
01:53:18,290 --> 01:53:20,700
知道我是什么造就的了
What I am made from.

1327
01:53:23,410 --> 01:53:28,040
我…我是尸骨堆里造出来的
I am… the child of a charnel house.

1328
01:53:31,330 --> 01:53:32,660
我是残骸
A wreckage.

1329
01:53:33,910 --> 01:53:37,200
是用垃圾和被丢弃的尸体拼凑出来的
Assembled from refuse and the discarded dead.

1330
01:53:43,910 --> 01:53:45,120
是怪物
A monster.

1331
01:53:46,700 --> 01:53:49,000
我知道你是谁
I know what you are.

1332
01:53:51,200 --> 01:53:52,330
你是个好人
A good man.

1333
01:53:53,200 --> 01:53:57,700
也是我的朋友
And… you are my friend.

1334
01:54:07,450 --> 01:54:08,620
朋友？
Friend?

1335
01:54:10,580 --> 01:54:11,750
朋友
Friend.

1336
01:54:14,830 --> 01:54:16,120
那是什么？
What is that thing?

1337
01:54:17,790 --> 01:54:19,660
是森林里的那东西吗？
The-- The thing from the woods?

1338
01:54:20,910 --> 01:54:22,000
你把他怎么了？
What have you done to him?

1339
01:54:24,330 --> 01:54:25,290
别动
Don't move.

1340
01:54:36,580 --> 01:54:38,910
快！上膛！杀了它！
Quick! Reload! Kill it!

1341
01:55:53,000 --> 01:55:55,040
一切重回寂静
There was silence again,

1342
01:55:56,330 --> 01:56:01,450
而冷酷无情的生活还将继续
and then… merciless life.

1343
01:56:16,870 --> 01:56:18,790
我死了多久？
How long did I die for?

1344
01:56:19,370 --> 01:56:20,660
不知道
I do not know.

1345
01:56:21,370 --> 01:56:23,660
但我看到身上的伤口愈合了
But I saw my injuries healed.

1346
01:56:24,750 --> 01:56:28,370
冬日的寒风直灌入肺
The cold winter air stung in my lungs.

1347
01:56:36,500 --> 01:56:39,620
孤独感更甚以往 且前所未有
I felt lonelier than ever,

1348
01:56:40,620 --> 01:56:45,450
因为对世人而言 治愈一切痛苦的良药
because for every man there was but one remedy to all pain:

1349
01:56:46,540 --> 01:56:51,160
唯有死亡 而这恩赐你也狠心剥夺
Death, a gift you too had denied me.

1350
01:56:52,040 --> 01:56:54,160
我的内心涌起羡慕之情
Envy rose within me

1351
01:56:55,080 --> 01:56:58,080
遂决意向你索求一份恩典
and decided to demand a single grace from you.

1352
01:56:59,330 --> 01:57:01,040
我的缔造者
My creator.

1353
01:57:02,370 --> 01:57:06,830
我想要…一个同伴
I would demand… a companion.

1354
01:57:33,540 --> 01:57:34,950
起来吧
I need you to get up.

1355
01:57:36,290 --> 01:57:37,830
好的
Yes, of course. Of course.

1356
01:57:37,910 --> 01:57:40,700
婚礼马上要开始了 你得陪在我身边
The wedding will start soon and I want you by my side.

1357
01:57:41,410 --> 01:57:42,700
要不是你天性善良
It's hard to believe,

1358
01:57:43,750 --> 01:57:45,750
我都不敢相信这话是你说的
if not for your kind nature.

1359
01:58:00,830 --> 01:58:03,200
我跟几位宾客说了调查的事
I've spoken to a few guests about the inquest.

1360
01:58:04,120 --> 01:58:05,200
关于那场爆炸的调查
About the explosion.

1361
01:58:07,000 --> 01:58:09,160
他们中的大多数都接受了官方的说法
The majority accept it for what it was.

1362
01:58:11,450 --> 01:58:13,450
官方怎么说 威廉？
And what was it, William?

1363
01:58:14,870 --> 01:58:15,950
都过去了 维克多
The past, Victor.

1364
01:58:17,620 --> 01:58:18,910
那是场可怕的意外
A terrible accident.

1365
01:58:26,290 --> 01:58:28,080
我想卖了那座庄园
I intend to sell the estate.

1366
01:58:31,500 --> 01:58:33,540
我们只有彼此了
All we have is each other.

1367
01:58:49,250 --> 01:58:51,160
往四面八方撒
I want you to throw the petals everywhere.

1368
01:58:51,250 --> 01:58:52,660
到处都撒一点
Throw them everywhere.

1369
01:58:55,200 --> 01:58:56,950
到楼上去 再多撒点
Go upstairs and do some more of that.

1370
01:59:06,370 --> 01:59:09,830
我知道 婚礼前见新娘会带来厄运
I know it is bad luck to see the bride before the ceremony.

1371
01:59:10,450 --> 01:59:11,660
只对新郎起效
Only for the groom.

1372
01:59:13,410 --> 01:59:14,950
没错 对我没用
Yes, that's right. Not for me.

1373
01:59:17,160 --> 01:59:18,370
你好啊 伊丽莎白
Hello, Elizabeth.

1374
01:59:21,290 --> 01:59:24,790
之前我从未感受过懊悔 而现在懊悔充斥了我的内心
I've rarely felt remorse before and now I feel little else. I…

1375
01:59:25,500 --> 01:59:29,660
我的心被一种冲动占据已久 但这种感觉已经消散
A fever gripped me for so long, but it has passed,

1376
01:59:29,750 --> 01:59:31,750
我可以正常地面对你了
and I see you now as I should.

1377
01:59:33,450 --> 01:59:37,620
无论如何 我衷心祝愿
For whatever it's worth, I… I wish you and my little brother,

1378
01:59:37,700 --> 01:59:40,410
你和我挚爱的弟弟幸福
who I love more than life, the very best.

1379
01:59:43,160 --> 01:59:45,120
你大可以自欺欺人
You may like to believe you do.

1380
01:59:49,160 --> 01:59:51,040
而我都害怕听见
And I dread to even hear it.

1381
01:59:55,200 --> 01:59:57,910
今天是我的大喜之日 我就求你一件事
On my wedding day, I ask you but for a single grace.

1382
01:59:59,160 --> 02:00:00,370
别撒谎了
No more lies.

1383
02:00:01,790 --> 02:00:04,000
-我想告诉你… -给我出去
-I-- I want to tell you-- -Leave my chambers now.

1384
02:00:04,080 --> 02:00:05,870
-伊丽莎白 -出去！
-Elizabeth. -Leave!

1385
02:01:00,080 --> 02:01:01,870
出来 别躲在暗处
Come out of the shadows,

1386
02:01:03,160 --> 02:01:04,450
如果你在这里
if you are here.

1387
02:01:21,910 --> 02:01:23,160
你是来感谢我的吗？
Are you here to thank me?

1388
02:01:23,750 --> 02:01:27,290
你活下来了 还变得足够聪明 都找到我了
You survived and are intelligent enough to have found me.

1389
02:01:29,290 --> 02:01:30,700
是我造得好
I made you well.

1390
02:01:30,790 --> 02:01:37,450
我要你给我造一个同伴
I need you to make a companion for me.

1391
02:01:38,160 --> 02:01:40,200
像我这样的
One like me.

1392
02:01:40,290 --> 02:01:42,000
同伴？
A com… A companion?

1393
02:01:48,040 --> 02:01:49,040
我知道了
I see.

1394
02:01:53,330 --> 02:01:54,660
再来个怪物
Another monster.

1395
02:01:55,330 --> 02:01:56,330
对
Yes.

1396
02:01:57,200 --> 02:01:59,370
让我们两个怪物作伴
We can be monsters together.

1397
02:02:02,580 --> 02:02:07,040
我付出巨大代价 才找回了理智
I have found sanity at such a cost,

1398
02:02:07,120 --> 02:02:11,500
你却想让我再回疯狂
and you here… are madness calling me back.

1399
02:02:11,580 --> 02:02:13,620
我死不了
I cannot die.

1400
02:02:17,250 --> 02:02:19,290
只有我自己
And I cannot live…

1401
02:02:21,910 --> 02:02:22,910
我也活不好
alone.

1402
02:02:24,160 --> 02:02:26,700
我造出了非常恐怖的东西
In you I have created something truly horrible.

1403
02:02:28,080 --> 02:02:29,950
不是东西
Not something.

1404
02:02:30,910 --> 02:02:32,660
是人
Someone.

1405
02:02:33,660 --> 02:02:36,830
你造出了人
You made someone.

1406
02:02:37,620 --> 02:02:38,540
就是我
Me.

1407
02:02:39,450 --> 02:02:42,250
不管我多么让人费解 但我会思考
Whatever puzzle I am, creator, I think.

1408
02:02:43,160 --> 02:02:44,410
有感受
I feel.

1409
02:02:45,870 --> 02:02:47,580
我只有这一个请求
I have this sole petition…

1410
02:02:48,450 --> 02:02:52,540
再造一个像我一样的
Make one like me.

1411
02:02:54,290 --> 02:02:55,410
然后呢？
And then what?

1412
02:02:56,500 --> 02:02:58,200
生育
Procreation.

1413
02:03:00,000 --> 02:03:01,620
繁殖
Reproduction.

1414
02:03:06,450 --> 02:03:07,620
建立家庭？
A home?

1415
02:03:08,540 --> 02:03:09,950
建造坟墓？
A grave?

1416
02:03:11,540 --> 02:03:15,250
死亡与破坏不断上演
Death begetting death begetting death.

1417
02:03:15,330 --> 02:03:17,580
恶魔的种族在地球上蔓延
A race of devils propagated upon the earth.

1418
02:03:17,660 --> 02:03:19,620
肮脏永不断绝
Obscenity perpetuating itself.

1419
02:03:20,410 --> 02:03:23,910
在你看来我很肮脏 在我看来我只是我
I am obscene to you, but to myself I simply am.

1420
02:03:24,000 --> 02:03:25,160
滚开！
Begone!

1421
02:03:27,620 --> 02:03:33,830
我绝不会再造一个 像你这么邪恶丑陋的东西
Never again will I make something like you, wicked and deformed.

1422
02:03:38,290 --> 02:03:44,330
这一切还不都是 源自你的执念 维克多
Then it is still all about your will, Victor.

1423
02:03:47,080 --> 02:03:52,410
凭恐怖的执念造就我 如今又固执地谴责我
That horrible, horrible will that birthed me condemns me now?

1424
02:03:53,700 --> 02:03:58,330
我开口说话算不上奇迹 你愿意倾听才算！
The miracle is not that I should speak, but that you would ever listen!

1425
02:04:02,080 --> 02:04:07,330
你不愿赐我伴侣 我将倾泻怒火
If you are not to award me love, then I will indulge in rage.

1426
02:04:07,410 --> 02:04:08,950
无穷无尽的怒火
And mine is infinite.

1427
02:04:15,200 --> 02:04:16,500
请让一让
Step aside.

1428
02:04:16,580 --> 02:04:17,500
维克多
Victor.

1429
02:04:18,870 --> 02:04:19,910
怎么了？
What's going on?

1430
02:04:38,660 --> 02:04:39,700
你
You…

1431
02:04:44,620 --> 02:04:45,500
你
You…

1432
02:04:46,660 --> 02:04:47,580
是你
It's you.

1433
02:04:52,870 --> 02:04:55,000
伊丽莎白 离它远一点！
Elizabeth, move away from it!

1434
02:04:55,700 --> 02:04:56,620
不要！
No!

1435
02:05:10,660 --> 02:05:13,500
那东西袭击了她！
It attacked her! It attacked her!

1436
02:05:32,950 --> 02:05:34,290
带我走吧
Take me with you.

1437
02:05:48,830 --> 02:05:49,910
天啊
Oh, my God!

1438
02:06:16,200 --> 02:06:18,500
别动 让我来…我能救你
No, let me… I can save you.

1439
02:06:18,580 --> 02:06:19,660
我会救活你
I can save you.

1440
02:06:20,330 --> 02:06:21,330
救我？
From what?

1441
02:06:22,410 --> 02:06:23,540
是害我吧
From you?

1442
02:06:25,330 --> 02:06:26,700
我怕你 维克多
I fear you, Victor.

1443
02:06:26,790 --> 02:06:27,910
不
No, no…

1444
02:06:28,000 --> 02:06:29,290
一直怕你
I always have.

1445
02:06:29,950 --> 02:06:32,410
你的每一次疯狂和破坏
Every ounce of madness and destruction.

1446
02:06:33,580 --> 02:06:37,160
如同大火 足以吞噬一切
The very conflagration that devoured everything.

1447
02:06:39,080 --> 02:06:40,450
一切都是你造成的
It all came from you.

1448
02:06:46,450 --> 02:06:47,950
你才是怪物
You are the monster.

1449
02:07:21,040 --> 02:07:23,200
我和这个世界格格不入
My place was never in this world.

1450
02:07:25,120 --> 02:07:29,450
我一直渴望并追寻着 一种说不清道不明的东西
I sought and longed for something I could not quite name.

1451
02:07:31,580 --> 02:07:33,450
可在你身上 我找到了这种东西
But in you, I found it.

1452
02:07:36,750 --> 02:07:39,200
丢失并被寻回
To be lost and to be found,

1453
02:07:40,200 --> 02:07:42,200
这就是爱的宿命
that is the lifespan of love.

1454
02:07:44,200 --> 02:07:45,620
其短暂
And in its brevity,

1455
02:07:46,870 --> 02:07:48,120
其悲剧性
its tragedy…

1456
02:07:52,200 --> 02:07:53,870
造就永恒
this has been made eternal.

1457
02:07:57,830 --> 02:08:00,870
就让我在你的注视之中
Better this way… to fade…

1458
02:08:03,290 --> 02:08:05,160
死去吧
with your eyes gazing upon me.

1459
02:08:48,200 --> 02:08:51,290
她走了 我也想随她而去
She is gone and I long to follow.

1460
02:08:56,120 --> 02:08:58,250
你给了我备受唾弃的生命
You gave me life unwanted.

1461
02:08:59,580 --> 02:09:01,410
我这就还给你
I give that back to you.

1462
02:09:02,200 --> 02:09:04,120
你当我是怪物
You thought me a monster.

1463
02:09:04,950 --> 02:09:06,580
就让我这个怪物来回敬你
Now I return the favor.

1464
02:09:12,370 --> 02:09:15,160
杀了我 现在就杀了我
Kill me! Kill me now, do it!

1465
02:09:16,410 --> 02:09:18,160
我要让你流血
I will make you bleed.

1466
02:09:19,000 --> 02:09:21,120
让你卑微求饶
I will make you humble.

1467
02:09:21,870 --> 02:09:23,540
你是造了我
You may be my creator,

1468
02:09:24,120 --> 02:09:27,950
但从今天起 你要听我的话
but from this day forward, I will be your master.

1469
02:10:08,040 --> 02:10:12,120
你为了猎杀我
You hunted me past the forests,

1470
02:10:12,950 --> 02:10:14,830
翻山越岭
past the mountains,

1471
02:10:15,540 --> 02:10:17,950
横跨冰川
past frozen horizons,

1472
02:10:19,080 --> 02:10:22,000
直到天地间
until there was nothing left.

1473
02:10:22,580 --> 02:10:25,620
只剩你我
Just you… and me.

1474
02:10:46,120 --> 02:10:47,040
给我来点子弹
I need ammunition.

1475
02:10:50,290 --> 02:10:51,700
这个磨快一点
Sharpen this.

1476
02:10:51,790 --> 02:10:54,160
来三罐炼乳 一点木柴
Three cans of condensed milk, some firewood.

1477
02:10:56,040 --> 02:10:57,500
还有六筒炸药
And six sticks of dynamite.

1478
02:10:57,580 --> 02:10:58,410
六筒？
Six?

1479
02:10:59,370 --> 02:11:00,620
你要打什么？
What are you hunting?

1480
02:11:02,250 --> 02:11:03,500
大的
Big game.

1481
02:12:11,500 --> 02:12:13,450
不！
No! No! No!

1482
02:12:22,330 --> 02:12:24,040
维克多
Victor.

1483
02:12:24,120 --> 02:12:27,160
只有被我伤到 你才会听我说话
You only listen when I hurt you.

1484
02:12:41,330 --> 02:12:44,870
这个 你相信这东西
This. You put your faith in this.

1485
02:12:44,950 --> 02:12:47,250
能够摧毁我
You think this will unmake me.

1486
02:12:51,700 --> 02:12:55,000
点着吧 希望如你所愿 但如果失败了
Light it then and hope it does, but if it does not,

1487
02:12:55,080 --> 02:12:57,160
我会再来找你
I will come for you again.

1488
02:12:57,790 --> 02:12:59,120
点起来！
Light it!

1489
02:13:06,700 --> 02:13:10,040
快跑吧
Now… run.

1490
02:13:47,120 --> 02:13:52,660
好了 如今你残破不堪
So, there you were, broken and discarded.

1491
02:13:53,750 --> 02:13:55,120
而我
And I,

1492
02:13:56,450 --> 02:13:58,250
又活过来了
alive again.

1493
02:14:03,040 --> 02:14:07,950
我能感到 被灼伤的血肉在重新生长
I could feel my singed flesh regrowing.

1494
02:14:08,790 --> 02:14:12,660
断裂的骨头重回原位
The crackling of my bones resetting.

1495
02:14:13,910 --> 02:14:20,250
永不停息的心脏泵出汩汩的血流
The murmur of my blood pumping through my incessant heart.

1496
02:14:21,370 --> 02:14:24,330
再次发现无人怜悯
And once more finding no mercy,

1497
02:14:25,830 --> 02:14:28,290
我只剩一条路可走
I had but one path.

1498
02:14:40,450 --> 02:14:42,200
我们终究走到了这一步
And here we are.

1499
02:14:44,620 --> 02:14:46,540
精疲力尽 一无所有
Spent and done.

1500
02:14:49,330 --> 02:14:52,660
再没有什么可以付出或索取了
No more in us to give or take.

1501
02:14:53,200 --> 02:14:54,620
帐篷外的血迹
The blood outside the tent…

1502
02:14:55,120 --> 02:14:56,160
是我的
It is mine.

1503
02:14:57,330 --> 02:14:58,790
都是我的
All mine.

1504
02:15:00,000 --> 02:15:01,290
我将流血
I will bleed.

1505
02:15:02,830 --> 02:15:03,700
疼痛
Ache.

1506
02:15:04,870 --> 02:15:06,000
受苦
Suffer.

1507
02:15:09,120 --> 02:15:11,950
永无尽头
You see, it will never end.

1508
02:15:31,910 --> 02:15:33,450
对不起
I am sorry.

1509
02:15:39,950 --> 02:15:42,000
我的内心充满懊悔
Regret consumes me.

1510
02:15:44,120 --> 02:15:46,660
如今我终于能正视我的生命了
And I now regard my life for what it was.

1511
02:15:49,160 --> 02:15:51,580
缔造者 你要走了
You will go now, creator.

1512
02:15:54,410 --> 02:15:56,000
要消失了
Fade away.

1513
02:15:58,700 --> 02:16:01,370
一切都只是短暂的一瞬
It will all be but a brief moment.

1514
02:16:03,040 --> 02:16:06,000
我的诞生 我的悲伤
My birth. My grief.

1515
02:16:06,910 --> 02:16:08,370
你的损失
Your loss.

1516
02:16:10,950 --> 02:16:13,200
我不会受惩罚
I will not be punished.

1517
02:16:14,660 --> 02:16:16,410
也无法摆脱罪责
Nor absolved.

1518
02:16:20,830 --> 02:16:22,160
我的希望
What hope I had,

1519
02:16:23,200 --> 02:16:24,750
我的怒火
what rage…

1520
02:16:26,540 --> 02:16:27,910
都毫无意义
It is all nothing.

1521
02:16:31,200 --> 02:16:35,660
那股造就我的浪潮 如今要带你走了
The tide that brought me here now comes to take you away.

1522
02:16:38,160 --> 02:16:39,500
留下搁浅的我
Leaving me stranded.

1523
02:16:47,790 --> 02:16:49,250
原谅我吧
Forgive me.

1524
02:16:51,250 --> 02:16:52,500
吾儿
My son.

1525
02:17:00,750 --> 02:17:05,410
如你有意 也请宽恕自己的存在
And if you have it in your heart, forgive yourself into existence.

1526
02:17:06,040 --> 02:17:10,410
吾儿 如果无法死去 还请细思此事
If death is not to be, then consider this, my son.

1527
02:17:11,080 --> 02:17:12,790
既然活着
While you are alive,

1528
02:17:13,660 --> 02:17:16,450
除了活下去 还有别的选择吗？
what recourse do you have but to live?

1529
02:17:23,870 --> 02:17:24,950
活着
Live.

1530
02:17:26,620 --> 02:17:27,870
说出我的名字吧
Say my name.

1531
02:17:29,700 --> 02:17:31,950
我的名字是父亲起的
My father gave me that name,

1532
02:17:33,120 --> 02:17:34,410
但其实并无意义
and it meant nothing.

1533
02:17:36,950 --> 02:17:39,250
现在 我请求你把这个名字还给我
Now I ask you to give it back to me…

1534
02:17:41,750 --> 02:17:43,120
最后一次了
one last time.

1535
02:17:44,950 --> 02:17:46,700
就像最开始 你把这个名字
The way you said it at the beginning.

1536
02:17:48,290 --> 02:17:50,580
当成全世界时那样呼唤我
When it meant the world to you.

1537
02:17:56,290 --> 02:17:57,500
维克多
Victor.

1538
02:18:00,500 --> 02:18:02,000
我宽恕你
I forgive you.

1539
02:18:25,080 --> 02:18:27,660
安息吧 父亲
Rest now, Father.

1540
02:18:32,160 --> 02:18:33,540
或许现在
Perhaps now,

1541
02:18:35,450 --> 02:18:37,540
我们都能算作是人了
we can both be human.

1542
02:18:47,370 --> 02:18:48,290
放下武器
Weapons down.

1543
02:18:49,000 --> 02:18:51,040
-放下武器 -我要为我的人负责
-Put the weapons down! -I am responsible for my men.

1544
02:18:52,450 --> 02:18:53,700
让他走
He can leave.

1545
02:20:28,580 --> 02:20:29,660
船能动了！
We are free!

1546
02:20:29,750 --> 02:20:31,000
我们自由了！
We are free!

1547
02:20:32,500 --> 02:20:33,790
船长
Captain…

1548
02:20:34,790 --> 02:20:36,160
您的指令是？
What are your orders?

1549
02:20:36,250 --> 02:20:37,250
扬帆起航
Man the sails.

1550
02:20:37,830 --> 02:20:38,700
掉头
Turn around.

1551
02:20:38,790 --> 02:20:40,080
您要亲自宣布吗？
Do you want to tell the men?

1552
02:20:40,700 --> 02:20:41,540
大家听好！
Men!

1553
02:20:42,950 --> 02:20:44,120
我们开船回家
We're sailing home!

1554
02:20:44,830 --> 02:20:45,910
我们回家了
We're sailing home!

1555
02:21:38,160 --> 02:21:43,700
（“心会破碎 但破碎后依然跳动” 拜伦勋爵）

1556
02:21:51,540 --> 02:21:52,540
（基于玛丽·雪莱）

1557
02:21:52,620 --> 02:21:55,120
（所著小说《科学怪人》改编）

1558
02:22:56,250 --> 02:22:59,870
《科学怪人》

1559
